#: ../../catalogs.rst:18
# 2324a82df196418f9fe3e47ec6011339
msgid "If you want *all* of your library cataloged, remove any search or filtering criteria in the main window. With a single book selected, all books in your library will be candidates for inclusion in the generated catalog. Individual books may be excluded by various criteria; see the :ref:`excluded_genres` section below for more information."
